{"id":22574,"type":4,"name":"The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/4e/b9/22574_LEMT1.jpg","rating":{"total":1340,"count":{"1":2,"2":0,"3":2,"4":3,"5":16,"6":49,"7":146,"8":383,"9":489,"10":250},"score":8.5},"summary":"　　《上古卷轴V：天际》（The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim）是由贝塞斯达软件公司开发的角色扮演游戏，是上古卷轴系列的第五作，于2011年11月11日发布，发布平台有Microsoft Windows、PlayStation 3和Xbox 360.\r\n\r\n　　《天际》的故事背景设定于前作《湮没》的200年后，天际省因至高王遇刺陷入内战，被诺德人奉为神的巨龙Alduin要摧毁整个世界。玩家扮演最后的龙裔，打败Alduin并拯救世界。\r\n\r\n　　天际采用了全新的引擎Creation Engine。新引擎整合了一些早已用于B社其他游戏如湮没和辐射3中的技术。Todd Howard称新引擎在角色和动作方面有较大的强化。新引擎的的特点还包括动态飘雪，风计算，适用于所有游戏中物体的阴影计算，改进的景深绘制。NPC能与环境交互，能对玩家的动作做出更真实的反应。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>上古卷轴V：天际</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/33481\">Bethesda Game Studios</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/10310\">Bethesda Softworks</a></li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/36795\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">Todd Howard</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>上古卷轴5</li><li><span>平台: </span>Nintendo Switch</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Xbox One</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS4</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Xbox 360</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS3</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>RPG</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>Creation Engine</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">游戏引擎: </span>Havok Physics</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>单人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2011年11月11日</li><li><span>售价: </span>$59.99</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.elderscrolls.com/</li><li><span>总监: </span>Todd Howard</li>","collection":{"wish":200,"collect":1362,"doing":214,"on_hold":180,"dropped":70},"tags":[{"name":"RPG","count":361},{"name":"膝盖中了一箭","count":265},{"name":"PC","count":228},{"name":"Bethesda","count":188},{"name":"老头滚动条5","count":152},{"name":"少女卷轴","count":135},{"name":"老滚5","count":121},{"name":"神作","count":95},{"name":"上古少女","count":67},{"name":"上瘾","count":61},